<headline>Heat Advisory issued August 01 at 2:14AM MDT until August 02 at 12:00AM MDT by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...HEAT ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL MIDNIGHT MDT TONIGHT...
* WHAT...Record hot temperatures of between 95 to 105 degrees at
lower elevations.
* WHERE...Portions of central, north central, southwest, and west
central Montana.
* WHEN...Until Midnight MDT tonight.
* IMPACTS...Hot temperatures may cause heat illnesses.</description>
<instruction>Drink plenty of fluids, stay in an air-conditioned room, stay out of
the sun, and check up on relatives and neighbors.</instruction>
